data.description: Come check out this inviting home in the serene setting of Spring Valley Ranch! This 5 bedroom, 4 bath 2-story home with finished basement & 3 car garage sits on a large corner lot. Upon entry you are greeted to a welcoming foyer that leads to plenty of spacious living areas , a main level bedroom perfect for guest stays and a full bath, on the other side of the entry is a bright dining room that can be used as an office space. Head toward the family room you will notice large windows and 2 story ceilings with an open concept layout connecting the kitchen & eating space & family room with a lovely fireplace to relax by. Gourmet kitchen with modern stainless appliances, plenty of storage & cabinet spaces, center island and a coffee bar /butlers pantry off the hall. The kitchen boasts a large walk in pantry as well as additional storage or mud room off kitchen into the garage. The large space currently fits two additional fridges!  Out the sliding glass doors you will find an inviting covered patio, large back yard, a trampoline and plenty of planter beds for the gardening enthusiast. Head upstairs to the second floor, where you'll find the luxurious primary suite, with two walk-in closets, and a five piece bath suite with a shower & large tub. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms (note the secondary bedroom is 2 bedrooms combined to make a great kids bedroom & play space), a large multipurpose loft perfect for relaxing , along with a full bathroom provide ample space on this level. Laundry located on 2nd floor. Fully finished basement, with open layout and generous space has a large 3/4 bathroom with heated floors , large bedroom & ample closet space (Or turn it into a craft room or gym ). Conveniently located close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining, this remarkable home offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own . Solar panels also a great addition to this home.
